1. Njih* dvoje su se zaljubili. (The two of them fell in love.)
2. Njihova* zadovoljstva bila je ogromna. (Their satisfaction was immense.)
3. Oni su se smijali njihovim* šalama. (They laughed at their jokes.)
4. Njihov* je život bio ispunjen radom. (Their life was filled with work.)
5. Njima* je trebalo puno vremena da se dogovore. (It took them a lot of time to agree.)